# Firebase (FCM) config. NOT a secret — it ships inside the APK and anyone can
# extract it. It is untracked because it binds a build to ONE Firebase project:
# Aul is self-hostable, so each operator brings their own project (or uses no
# push at all — the server boots fine without it). See docs/RELEASE.md.
